data.description: Lovely 2BR 1 Bath ranch home in Hampton is waiting for the right person to call this home. This home was fully renovated in 2019. It features a newer roof, newer AC, newer LVP flooring in the kitchen, newer gas range, newer water heater and newer kitchen counters. This home is centrally located in Hampton and is close to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Ideal home for someone looking for one floor living, first time homebuyer, or an investor. Seller will provide 1year home warranty with acceptable offer.
